    <PackageReleaseNotes>[General]
+ Code performance and reliability improved thanks to FxCop Analyzers.
+ Missing XML for some new modules added.
+ Replace structs by TupleValue to reduce load pressure on GC.
+ Add new dependencies [ExcelDataReader] for File module excel reader which should not bring any huge drawback since this library is lightweight as well as Utilities.

[File]
+ Add excel file reader.
- Remove generic constraint from all write-related methods.

[Data.Enumerable]
+ Add Partition method which behavior similar to list.Partition in F#.

[HttpRequest]
- Remove some complex overload methods which often confuses on how to use, result in a little bit back-to-tradition way when consume the function.



</PackageReleaseNotes>
